<!-- 
PAYMENT ROUTING LOGIC:

1. Alby Hub / LND wallets (support keysend):
   - Alice Host: pays 02eec7245d6b7d2ccb30380bfbe2a3648cd7a942653f5aa340edcea1f283686619 (keysend)
   - Bob Host: pays 03a0434d9e47f3c86235477c7b1ae6ae5d3442d49b1943c2b752a68e2a47e247c7 (keysend)
   - Producer Carol: pays carol@walletofsatoshi.com (Lightning address)
   - Podcast Index: pays 02d5c1bf8b940dc9cadca86d1b0a3c37fbe39cee4c7e839e33bef9174531d27f52 (keysend)

2. Primal / Coinos wallets (no keysend support):
   - Alice Host: pays alice@getalby.com (Lightning address fallback)
   - Bob Host: pays bob@getalby.com (Lightning address fallback) 
   - Producer Carol: pays carol@walletofsatoshi.com (Lightning address)
   - Podcast Index: SKIPPED (no Lightning address fallback provided)

3. Benefits:
   - Keysend-capable wallets use preferred method (lower fees, faster)
   - Non-keysend wallets can still participate in value4value
   - Podcasters control which recipients get fallback options
   - No dependency on proxy services like TSB
   - Clean, standards-compliant RSS implementation
-->